Compatible with multiple API driven stats sources and providers, Match Centre serves real-time match day stats, match timelines (commentary), team line-ups and live scoring before, during and after matches, providing a comprehensive second-screen option for fans - inside and outside the stadium. “We realised we could provide a truly subversive experience for fans – a digital destination on match days that captures the angst, excitement and elation of live sport” - Clinton Bosch, PT SportSuite CEO With multi-channel fan engagement on match days having become one of the most important strategic objectives for leagues, tournaments and clubs – Match Centre integrates with match-related news content, 3rd party retail and ticketing services, and PT SportSuite’s proprietary fan engagement Challenges platform that asks supporters to capture and share their match day experience. Together with sponsors, sports organisations can make fan media exchange part of the at-home or in-stadium match day experience by activating branded fan UGC campaigns. The new Match Centre module extends PT SportSuite’s mobile app and web framework that also offers: User registration via SSO Multi-tenant (team) or single-brand configurability Related news and media via API Player and team profiles with stats API integration Video OTT (live and on-demand) Dynamic advertising and monetisation Social feed integrationClinton Bosch, PT SportSuite CTO, says: “Having listened to the needs of the market, and those of our current partners and customers, we realised we could provide a truly subversive experience for fans – a digital destination on match days that captures the angst, excitement and elation of live sport, while creating a ‘digital moment in time’ after the final whistle has blown. “PT's Match Centre leverages off our ability to integrate multiple data sources into a single API middle-tier, to cater for multiple providers and subscribers of stats data and provide a truly agnostic stats engine across web and app. Together with our Fan UGC Challenge module makes Match Centre a compelling digital offering.” Ready for a team talk? Book a demo to learn more about PT SportSuite’s web and app modules.